headline: What Factors Are Shaping the New Narrative for Oracle?
summary: Oracle’s consensus analyst price target has recently surged from $253.13 to $333.49, reflecting a wave of renewed optimism from Wall Street. This dramatic increase is largely fueled by extraordinary growth in Oracle’s cloud business, which has achieved record-breaking bookings driven by AI demand and major long-term contracts.
